{ "id": 103249687,"title":"Modern Designer Furnished Apartment in the EUROPALACE Building","price":"292000","description":"This modern, designer-furnished apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building offers views of the beautiful Little Fatra, Martinky, Dubeň, including Vlčince and the surrounding area thanks to its elevated position. The apartment is sensibly divided into a living (social) area and a space designated for relaxation or study. The total associated area is 94.93 m2, which consists of : entrance hallway / 6.82 m2 / with a built-in wardrobe measuring 3 meters, making storage in the apartment hassle-free, southeast-facing living room with kitchen / up to 25.56 m2 /, offering views of the Little Fatra and Martinky, providing beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The living room is connected to the kitchen, aesthetically separated by a feature ceiling that also houses the lighting fixtures, t has access to a balcony that runs the entire width of the living room, the bedroom (18.9 m2) is furnished with a double bed, nightstands, and wardrobes, and boasts an ideal location that new owners will appreciate, especially in the summer months, as it is north-facing, preventing overheating when watching TV or having guests. The apartment also features a spacious brick shower enclosure with storage ledge, a bespoke kitchen unit with built-in appliances (induction hob, BOSCH dishwasher) and (oven, Electrolux microwave), a carbon extractor hood from the FRANKE brand, a sliding kitchen table with designer base that can serve as a workspace while cooking, as well as a dining table during dinner. The apartment is equipped with LED lighting options, including a single remote control for all. The property also offers high-quality wood - aluminum windows, which provide thermal insulation but also effectively soundproof the apartment from outside environments. The apartment is located in a highly sought-after area, offering complete civic amenities and many additional benefits. The EUROPALACE complex itself offers premium services: the entire property is monitored 24 hours a day by a security service (SBS), with camera surveillance and monitoring of common areas, underground parking, and more. The building itself houses a restaurant, a dental clinic, a client center of the Ministry of Interior of the Slovak Republic, as well as the headquarters of our real estate agency MGM. It is just a few minutes' walk to grocery stores (Kaufland, LIDL), Dubeň shopping center, restaurants, primary and nursery schools, fitness facilities, ŽILPO polyclinic, and the University of Žilina. Tennis courts, an indoor swimming pool, a summer swimming pool, an athletic complex, and the Chrasť forest park sports and recreation zone are just a short distance away. The city center of Žilina is within a 5-minute drive, or a 15-minute walk. Direct access to the expressway connecting the routes Bratislava - Košice - Čadca is available within 3 minutes. public transport stops are located 50 m from the main entrance of the building."}
